@startuml Live_Data_Table_Realtime_Update
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam BoxPadding 10

title Live Data Table Real-time Update Sequence

participant "STM32" as STM32
participant "ESP32" as ESP32
participant "MQTT Broker" as MQTT
participant "app.js" as AppJS
participant "Browser" as Browser

note over STM32,ESP32: Periodic measurement
STM32 -> ESP32: Send sensor data (JSON)
activate ESP32
ESP32 -> MQTT: Publish(periodicData)
deactivate ESP32
activate MQTT
MQTT -> AppJS: Forward message
deactivate MQTT
activate AppJS

AppJS -> AppJS: handleMQTTMessage(topic, payload)
AppJS -> AppJS: Parse JSON
AppJS -> AppJS: Extract {time, temp, humi, mode, status}

AppJS -> AppJS: addToLiveDataTable(data)
AppJS -> AppJS: liveDataBuffer.unshift(entry)

AppJS -> AppJS: Check buffer length

alt Length > 100
    AppJS -> AppJS: liveDataBuffer.pop()\nRemove oldest entry
end

AppJS -> AppJS: Get filter selection\nfilter = #liveDataFilter.value

AppJS -> AppJS: Apply filter

alt Filter = "all"
    AppJS -> AppJS: filtered = liveDataBuffer
else Filter = "success"
    AppJS -> AppJS: filtered = buffer.filter\n(d => d.status == 'success')
else Filter = "error"
    AppJS -> AppJS: filtered = buffer.filter\n(d => d.status == 'error')
end

AppJS -> AppJS: Check filtered length

alt Empty
    AppJS -> Browser: innerHTML = "No data available"
    activate Browser
    deactivate Browser
else Has Data
    loop For each entry in filtered
        AppJS -> AppJS: Format time\nHH:MM:SS
        AppJS -> AppJS: Format status badge

        alt Status = "success"
            AppJS -> AppJS: Badge: connected "✓ Success"
        else Status = "error"
            AppJS -> AppJS: Badge: disconnected "✗ Error"
        end

        AppJS -> AppJS: Build table row\n<tr>#, time, temp, humi, mode, badge</tr>
    end

    AppJS -> Browser: Render to #liveDataTable\ntbody.innerHTML = rows
    activate Browser
    deactivate Browser
end

AppJS -> Browser: Update #liveDataCount\ntextContent = filtered.length
activate Browser
deactivate Browser

AppJS -> AppJS: Refresh Feather icons\nfeather.replace()

AppJS -> Browser: Table updated (real-time)
activate Browser
deactivate Browser
deactivate AppJS

note over AppJS,Browser: User interacts with table

alt User changes filter
    Browser -> AppJS: Change event
    activate AppJS
    AppJS -> AppJS: renderLiveDataTable()\nRe-filter and re-render
    AppJS -> Browser: Updated table
    activate Browser
    deactivate Browser
    deactivate AppJS
end

alt User clicks "Clear Table"
    Browser -> AppJS: Click event
    activate AppJS
    AppJS -> AppJS: Confirm dialog

    alt User confirms
        AppJS -> AppJS: liveDataBuffer = []
        AppJS -> AppJS: renderLiveDataTable()
        AppJS -> Browser: Empty table\naddStatus("Live data cleared")
        activate Browser
        deactivate Browser
    end
    deactivate AppJS
end

alt User clicks "Export CSV"
    Browser -> AppJS: Click event
    activate AppJS

    alt Buffer empty
        AppJS -> Browser: Show warning\n"No data to export"
        activate Browser
        deactivate Browser
    else Buffer has data
        AppJS -> AppJS: Build CSV\nHeaders + rows
        AppJS -> Browser: Create Blob
        activate Browser
        AppJS -> Browser: Trigger download\nlivedata_{timestamp}.csv
        deactivate Browser
        AppJS -> AppJS: addStatus("Live data exported")
    end
    deactivate AppJS
end

@enduml